data.description: Do not miss the opportunity to live in the sought after River Hills golf community. Wake up and enjoy your coffee on your deck overlooking the golf course. Or sit and enjoy the quiet on your front porch swing. This home has four bedrooms with a Master Suite on the 1st floor. And a second Master Suite upstairs. Formal dining room has been used as an additional family room, but can be converted back if desired. Hidden in an upstairs bedroom closet is the entrance door to extra floored storage space!  HOA allows fences and private pools in this community. With plenty of room in the driveway for your cars, come see this home for yourself!   The pool and clubhouse amenities are optional for a fee.  *Measurements are approximate and to be verified by buyer*
